This paper presents a new machine learning technique for training small resource-constrained predictors. The paper focuses on the algorithmic aspect of machine learning and does not involve any specific application domain. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SD (Software Engineering), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
